    - obs[16:19]: 3D angular velocity of the torso
    - obs[19:27]: 8 joint angular velocities

    Key indicators for rewards:
    - torso_z_pos = observation[0]
    - torso_x_velocity = observation[13]

    ## Episode End
    The ant is said to be unhealthy if the z-position of the torso is no longer contained in the healthy_z_range (0.2 to 1.0).
    The episode ends (terminates) when the ant becomes unhealthy or flips.

    def _get_obs(self):
